
  Toxapex    Poison Type Pokémon

  Toxapex crawls along the ocean 
  floor on its 12 legs.  It leaves 
  a trail of Corsola bits scattered 
  in its wake. 
	Evolution Chain
      Mareanie ► Toxapex

